WEBVTT

00:07:28.666 --> 00:07:31.079
they are all rigid responses.

00:07:32.586 --> 00:07:34.666
And if there's a single
lesson we can learn

00:07:34.690 --> 00:07:37.483
from the inevitable fall of apartheid

00:07:37.507 --> 00:07:40.192
it is that rigid denial doesn't work.

00:07:41.642 --> 00:07:42.992
It's unsustainable.

00:07:43.967 --> 00:07:46.831
For individuals, for families,

00:07:46.855 --> 00:07:48.005
for societies.

00:07:48.783 --> 00:07:52.863
And as we watch the ice caps melt,

00:07:52.887 --> 00:07:55.593
it is unsustainable for our planet.

00:07:57.831 --> 00:07:59.696
Research on emotional suppression shows

00:07:59.720 --> 00:08:02.688
that when emotions
are pushed aside or ignored,